{"course_code": "CRIM402", "total_reviews": 6, "instructors": [{"professor_id": "59555", "professor_name": "Gail Anderson", "avg_rating": 4.0, "avg_difficulty": 3.0, "review_count": 2, "reviews": [{"rating": 3.0, "difficulty": 4.0, "course_code": "CRIM402", "date": "Jul 10th, 2025", "metadata": {"For Credit": "Yes", "Attendance": "Not Mandatory", "Would Take Again": "", "Grade": "A-", "Textbook": "Yes"}, "review_msg": "Gail is super knowledgeable and has had a really impressive career. But unfortunately, this class was quite painful. Although the lecture videos were engaging, there are so many side assignments/discussions to complete weekly. There was no midterm, but the final exam was 120 short answer questions to complete in 3 hours. Literally impossible!!!!!!!", "helpful": 0, "not_helpful": 0, "tags": ["Lots of homework", "Lecture heavy", "Test heavy"]}, {"rating": 5.0, "difficulty": 2.0, "course_code": "CRIM402", "date": "Apr 15th, 2025", "metadata": {"For Credit": "Yes", "Attendance": "Not Mandatory", "Would Take Again": "Yes", "Grade": "Not sure yet", "Textbook": "N/A"}, "review_msg": "Such an interesting course and a prof which makes it so easy to understand and follow along. Clear instructions, assignments to be completed weekly but it's manageable. Would recommend this prof!!!", "helpful": 0, "not_helpful": 0, "tags": ["Clear grading criteria"]}]}, {"professor_id": "2382072", "professor_name": "Haley Goren", "avg_rating": 1.0, "avg_difficulty": 2.0, "review_count": 1, "reviews": [{"rating": 1.0, "difficulty": 2.0, "course_code": "CRIM402", "date": "Apr 8th, 2019", "metadata": {"For Credit": "Yes", "Attendance": "Mandatory", "Would Take Again": "No", "Grade": "B+", "Textbook": "Yes"}, "review_msg": "Not great", "helpful": 0, "not_helpful": 0, "tags": ["Tough grader"]}]}, {"professor_id": "2157448", "professor_name": "Momoko Ueda", "avg_rating": 2.0, "avg_difficulty": 5.0, "review_count": 2, "reviews": [{"rating": 3.0, "difficulty": 5.0, "course_code": "CRIM4